---
tags:
  - proxmox
  - proxmox/node
type: proxmox/node
node_name: "{{ node.node }}"
status: "{{ node.status | default('unknown') }}"
cpu_cores: {{ node.maxcpu | default(0) }}
memory_gb: {{ mem_total_gb }}
last_synced: "{{ synced_at }}"
---

# {{ node.node }}

{% if node.status | default('unknown') == 'online' %}
> [!success] Node Online
> {{ node.node }} is running. Uptime: {{ uptime_str }}.
{% elif node.status | default('unknown') == 'offline' %}
> [!danger] Node Offline
> {{ node.node }} is not responding.
{% else %}
> [!warning] Node Status: {{ node.status | default('unknown') }}
> Status could not be determined.
{% endif %}

## Status

| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Status | {{ node.status | default("N/A") }} |
| Uptime | {{ uptime_str }} |
| CPU | {{ node.cpu | default(0) | round(2) }}% ({{ node.maxcpu | default("N/A") }} cores) |
| Memory | {{ mem_used_gb }} GB / {{ mem_total_gb }} GB ({{ mem_pct }}%) |
| Root Disk | {{ disk_used_gb }} GB / {{ disk_total_gb }} GB ({{ disk_pct }}%) |
| Kernel | {{ node_status.kversion | default("N/A") }} |
| PVE Version | {{ node_status.pveversion | default("N/A") }} |

